            <div class="lp-element lp-pom-text nlh" id="lp-pom-text-10"><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">Thank you for your interest in our firm. Unfortunately, We are unable to further pursue any claim on your behalf.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 20px;">Please understand that this does not mean that a meritorious claim does not exist, it simply means that based on our criteria this is not a case we are able to pursue.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">As with all cases, different firms have different acceptance criteria and we therefore strongly recommend that you seek out another firm to review your case and provide you with a second opinion as quickly as is possible.</span><br><br></p><p><br><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div><div class="lp-element lp-pom-box" id="lp-pom-box-22"><div id="lp-pom-box-22-color-overlay"></div><div class="lp-element lp-pom-text nlh" id="lp-pom-text-23"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 45px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 48px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">WE ARE SORRY...</span></strong></p></div></div><div class="lp-element lp-pom-text nlh" id="lp-pom-text-32"><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">The particular facts and circumstances of your case can vary when the statute of limitations begins to run.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">This means if you do not file a lawsuit within the time established by law, your claim will be barred forever regardless of its merit.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">Therefore, we strongly recommend that you seek out counsel IMMEDIATELY, to assist you in the determination of your statute of limitations and in the prosecution of your case, should you wish to continue moving forward.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">Simply put, DO NOT DELAY seeking out an alternate attorney to review your case.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;">We appreciate your interest in our firm and regret that we will not be able to represent you in this matter.</span></p><p><br></p><p draggable="false"><span style="font-size: 20px;">If we can be of assistance in the future, we would certainly welcome the opportunity to be of service.</span></p></div>
